7bo6b4o2bobobo$5bobobo7bo5bo6b2ob3o$6b4o8b2o10bob2o$6bo3bo16bo$6b5o13b
2o$9bobo12bobo$10bo14b4o$25bo3bo$25b5o$28bo$29bo6$15b4o$19bo2$17bo22$b
